{
  "stem": "15732.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The system was-- subject were completely differently taught than in Romania, certainly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had to study Russian, Russian literature, Russian language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- the point I mostly disliked about school was that the headmaster wanted very often to encourage us to talk about our parents-- what they do at home, if they speak against the-- the system.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That, in other words, they wanted us to [? dop ?] in the-- our parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took it all with a lot of resentment, certainly that nobody would speak against one's parents and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at the-- I think that the second half of 1940, they started to deport people from Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The mood in the Jewish community was one of rising apprehension.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as I said before, there is not much that we can-- could have done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the-- we knew that Hitler is approaching fast, because after Austria came Czechloslovakia, and then came Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we feared what is going to be the-- the future.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The big world did not want Jewish refugees, not England, not France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Their visas were refused.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So all we were like trapped animals in a-- in a tub.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I must confess that nobody knew the full extent of what Hitler is doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I suppose that the biggest annihilation started which-- later, too, but it was enough we knew what had happened in Vienna, we knew what had happened in Prague.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- but as I said before, there was some sort of a-- a passivity that was born out of the political situation that we didn't have a way out, or were as if trapped in that point-- in-- in that place, and there was no way out.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
